target: TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_CALL_RETAINER_FAILED<tab> リテイナーを呼び出すことができませんでした。

source: TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_CALL_FAILED_NO_CHARGE<tab>The retainer managing this mannequin has been released from service. To access this mannequin, place it again and assign a new retainer.
target: TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_CALL_FAILED_NO_CHARGE<tab>契約切れのリテイナーを呼び出すことはできません。

source: TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_CHANGE_STATUS_DISABLE<tab>You must remove all gear from the mannequin before changing its settings.
target:
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_CHANGE_STATUS_DISABLEマネキンの設定を変更する場合、
販売中・展示中の装備品を、すべて外す必要があります。

source: TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_SELL_DISABLE<tab>You must remove all gear from the mannequin before you can list items for sale.
target:
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_SELL_DISABLE装備品を販売する場合、
展示中の装備品を、すべて外す必要があります。

source: TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_DISPLAY_DISABLE<tab>You must remove all gear from the mannequin before you can list items to display.
target:
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_DISPLAY_DISABLE装備品を展示する場合、
販売中の装備品を、すべて外す必要があります。

source: TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE1<tab>I have come, <var 08 E905 ((Mistress)) ((Master)) /var>.
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE2<tab>Nothin' fer ye to worry about.
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE3<tab>You summoned?
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE4<tab>Yes? <sigh> I hope this doesn't take long...
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE5<tab>You wish to see how a master handles a bazaar?
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE6<tab>Hello, hello! You called?
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>At your service, my <var 08 E905 ((lady)) ((lord)) /var>.
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>What's it to be this time, love?
target: TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>アタシを呼んで、何させようってんだい？

source: TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>What would you ask?
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>I'm so sorry to keep you waiting, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>. So very, very sorry.
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>Quickly now, I've places to be.
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>Well, if it ain't my favorite client! Always a pleasure, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>!
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE1<tab>Yes, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>? What is your bidding?
target: TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE1<tab>駆け付けました、ご用をどうぞ。

source: TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE2<tab>What's on the agenda, chief? Deprivin' saps o' their hard-earned gil?
target: TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE2<tab>貴様、くだらん用で呼んだのではあるまいな。

source: TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE3<tab>I have come. You may proceed.
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE4<tab>Oh, hello there. To what do I owe the pleasure?
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE5<tab>I am come to conduct business, and only business.

TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE6<tab>You look to be in good health, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>. How may I assist you this fine <var 08 E3E90C0D ((<var 08 E3E90C05 ((eve)) ((morn)) /var>)) ((<var 08 E3E90C12 ((day)) ((eve)) /var>)) /var>?
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>What is it you would have me do, <var 08 E905 ((milady)) ((milord)) /var>?
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>Usually, it's me doin' the summons and others doin' the waitin'.
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>Is there something that I can help you with?
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>Oh, why must you summon me at a time like this...?
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>I'm sure there is a perfectly good explanation for this summons.
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>You know, I thought you might be along to summon me. You may rest assured that I am ready and eager to serve.
target:
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE6呼び出されるんじゃないかな～って気がしてたんだよね。
準備ばんたんだよ！

source: TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE1<tab>Hail to thee, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>. Your humble servant has heard your summons.
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE2<tab>Greetin's and salutations, <var 08 E905 ((milady)) ((milord)) /var>. Pray speak yer desires, an' I'll do me damndest to see 'em done.
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE3<tab>I was wondering when you'd get around to calling me.
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE4<tab>Mind if we keep this brief? I've got a pretty little thing that's waitin' for me.
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE5<tab>What?
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE6<tab>I'm here, I'm here!
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>Here I am, <var 08 E905 ((Mistress)) ((Master)) /var>, as per your request.
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>'Ello, dearie. What's on the docket?
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>I never miss a chance to line these pockets.
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>Well, this is unexpected! What'll it be?
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>What is it now?
target: TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>お願いを聞いてあげました。

source: TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>Here I aaaaaam!
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE1<tab>How may I be of serrrvice, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>?
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE2<tab>It's a war out there, <var 08 E905 ((miss)) ((sir)) /var>. You have no idea.
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE3<tab>...
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE4<tab>Business or pleasure?
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE5<tab>I presume you did not summon me solely for the pleasure of my company.
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE6<tab>Just the <var 08 E905 ((fair maiden)) ((handsome fellow)) /var> I was hoping to see! Tell me your heart's desire.
target: TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE6<tab>呼んでもらって、うれしいよ。

source: TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>I hope your catcall is not one of disapproval.
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>Ye rang, <var 08 E905 ((milady)) ((milord)) /var>?
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>A cat's ears do not miss much―least of all a summons.
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>Curiosity called the cat. What do you have for me today?
target:
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE4あのぉ……
もしかして呼びました……？

source: TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>Ready when you are.
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>I was just thinking of you!
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE1<tab>What need have you of me today, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>?
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE2<tab>Bwahahaha! Ye got work needs gettin' done? Just point me in the right bloody direction.
target: TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE2<tab>わはは、みんなまとめて面倒みちゃるぞ！

source: TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE3<tab>I've come. What is it?
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE4<tab>Hey there─hic─<var 08 E905 ((missy)) ((mate)) /var>! Care to join me fer a pint?
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE5<tab>Couldn't come no quicker. Where's the work?
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE6<tab>I came runnin' soon as I heard the bell! Ye need somethin', chief?
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>I am at your disposal, <var 08 E905 ((milady)) ((milord)) /var>.
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>Ye got somethin' fer me, cap'n?
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>Go ahead, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>.
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>Let's keep this short and sweet, shall we?
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>This wouldn't be necessary if you entrusted your financial affairs to me.
target: TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>ワタシの仕事ぶりを手本にするがいい。

source: TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>So─sellin', buyin', drinkin', whorin'? What's it to be today?
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_AURA_MALE_TYPE1<tab>Greetings, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>. How may I be of service?
target:
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_AURA_MALE_TYPE1よぉ、！
今日はどんなことをしようか！

source: TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_AURA_MALE_TYPE2<tab>What'll it be, <var 08 E905 ((miss)) ((mate)) /var>?
target: TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_AURA_MALE_TYPE2<tab>遠慮は無用、なんでも言いな！

source: TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_AURA_MALE_TYPE3<tab>State your business.
target:
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_AURA_MALE_TYPE3我輩の名を呼ぶとは……。
フッ……貴様もたいがい、命知らずなものだ。

source: TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_AURA_MALE_TYPE4<tab>And how does this wonderful <var 08 E3E90C0D ((<var 08 E3E90C05 ((evening)) ((day)) /var>)) ((<var 08 E3E90C12 ((day)) ((evening)) /var>)) /var> find you?
target:
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_AURA_MALE_TYPE4やぁ、元気にしてたか？
お前さんの顔が見れて嬉しいよ。

source: TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_AURA_MALE_TYPE5<tab>Well... Here I am...<var 08 E905 ((Mistress)) ((Master)) /var>.
target:
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_AURA_MALE_TYPE5ったく……何の用だよ。
あんま、面倒な注文すんじゃねーぞ？

source:
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_AURA_MALE_TYPE6We work the market stalls,♪
And our uniforms are pretty;♪
We are sober men and true,♪
And attentive to our duties!♪
target:
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_AURA_MALE_TYPE6呼ばれたそばから、即見参ッ！
我が主よ、何か良いことはあったか？

source: TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab><var 08 E905 ((My lady)) ((My lord)) /var>. What would you ask of me?
target:
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE1お呼びですか、。
ご用件を承りますね！

source: TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>So. We doing this?
target: TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>呼んだからには、何か用なんだろうねえ？

source: TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>Yes?
target:
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE3この私をお呼びのようね。
さあ、あなたの用件を言いなさい。

source: TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>Hey, it's...it's you! Hello again, you!
target: TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>は～い、お変わりありませんか～？

source: TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>I-It's not like I want to sell your items or anything.
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>What do you have for me? Come on, come on! Don't be shy!
target:
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE6やっほー！
なになに、わたしに会いたかったの～？

source: TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE1<tab>You rang, <var 08 E905 ((milady)) ((milord)) /var>?
target:
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE1来たぞ、。
さて、なにをご所望かな？

source: TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE2<tab>I trust this will be worth my while.
target:
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE2……オレに用があるんだろ？
とっとと言いな、変な気ィ使うもんじゃねぇ。

source: TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE3<tab><var 1A 02 /var>What<var 1A 01 /var>?
target:
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE3俺様を呼びつけるか……。
余程の用件でなくば、許さんぞ？

source: TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE4<tab>Whatever you need, leave it to me! I have my methods.
target:
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE4やぁ主殿、世話になっているな。
さて今日は、何を任せてくれるのかな？

source: TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE5<tab>Gahaha! If it isn't my favorite <var 08 E905 ((mistress)) ((master)) /var>!
target:
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE5おうおうおうおう！
呼び付けたからには、バシッと頼みを聞かせやがれッ！

source: TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE6<tab>It is I, your most loyal and capable retainer!
target:
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE6チ～ッス！
オレのこと、呼びましたぁ？

source: TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>What will it be, love?
target:
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE1ハァイ、ハニー♪
今日はアタシにどんなご用？

source: TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>Your orders! I would hear them at once!
target:
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE2何の用だぁ？
今日もアツい話、よこしてくれよな！

source: TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>If there is something you would ask of me, then ask it.
target:
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE3汝、何を求むるか。
欲する望みをば、この耳に聞かせん……。

source: TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>Yes...? Is there something you─<yawn>─need?
target:
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE4はぁいぃ……ふわぁ～。
キミに呼ばれたかなぁ……それとも夢ぇ？

source: TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>A task for me? I hope it's something fun!
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>I am here to do your every bidding, <var 08 E905 ((Mistress)) ((Master)) /var>! Ask of me anything at all!
target:
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE6お呼びいただきましたかしら！？
わたくし、お役に立ってみせますわよ？

source: TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_VIERA_MALE_TYPE1<tab>I have been awaiting your summons, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>. What would you have of me this fine <var 08 E3E90C0D ((<var 08 E3E90C05 ((evening)) ((morning)) /var>)) ((<var 08 E3E90C12 ((day)) ((evening)) /var>)) /var>?
target:
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_VIERA_MALE_TYPE1やぁ、呼んでくれるのを待ってたよ！
今日は何を任せてくれるのかな？

source: TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_VIERA_MALE_TYPE2<tab>What can I do for ye, yer <var 08 E905 ((ladyship)) ((lordship)) /var>?
target:
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_VIERA_MALE_TYPE2お疲れさまッす、！！
自分がお役に立てるっすか！？

source: TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_VIERA_MALE_TYPE3<tab>You called, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>...?
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_VIERA_MALE_TYPE4<tab>You─hic─rang?
target:
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_VIERA_MALE_TYPE4うぃっく……
もしかして、呼んだぁ～？

source: TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_VIERA_MALE_TYPE5<tab>Need my assistance, do you? Let's make this quick, then.
target:
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_VIERA_MALE_TYPE5わざわざ、オレを呼んだの？
付き合ってやるから、早く聞かせなよ。

source: TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_VIERA_MALE_TYPE6<tab>You have my ear, <var 08 E905 ((milady)) ((milord)) /var>. Both of them, in fact!
target:
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_ENTER_VIERA_MALE_TYPE6やぁ主さん、世話になってるね！
いやはや、今日はどういった御用向きで？

source: TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE1<tab>If that is all, I will take my leave now, <var 08 E905 ((Mistress)) ((Master)) /var>.
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE2<tab>Take care o' yerself, hear?
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE3<tab>Until we next meet.
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE4<tab>Well, it's about time. Good-bye.
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE5<tab>I believe thanks are in order.
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE6<tab>I'm off, then!
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>With your leave, my <var 08 E905 ((lady)) ((lord)) /var>.
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>Don't you worry 'bout a thing. I got this.
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>Farewell, then.
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>If there is nothing else, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>, I'll be going now.
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>Is that all? Very well, until next time.
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>Oh, will that be all today? Very well, but promise me you'll come back soon!
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE1<tab>As always, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>, it has been an honor and a privilege.
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE2<tab>You can count on me, chief─I know how to get things done.
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE3<tab>Don't be a stranger.
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE4<tab>I swear it shall be done. Eventually.
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE5<tab>As you wish.
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE6<tab>Capital! I shall carry out your orders forthwith.
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>I humbly await your next summons, <var 08 E905 ((milady)) ((milord)) /var>.
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>Don't leave me alone for too long, hear?
target: TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>いつでも、頼りにしなさいね。

source: TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>Always a pleasure.
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>That will be all, yes? Then if you would excuse me...
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>I believe that concludes our dealings for now.
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>Are you certain you don't desire anything else? Anything at all? Very well, I shall take my leave.
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE1<tab>Your every whim shall be swiftly carried out with due care and consideration.
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE2<tab>Shouldn't take more than a moment, <var 08 E905 ((milady)) ((milord)) /var>.
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE3<tab>I'll be going, then.
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE4<tab>Thank the gods we're finished. I've got plans to put my hands in places I've never seen...if you know what I mean.
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE5<tab>Be well.
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE6<tab>I'm off, I'm off!
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>Until we meet again!
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>Blessin's o' the Twelve upon ye.
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>May Nald'thal see fit to fatten our pockets!
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>Very good, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>! Your wish is my command, and so forth.
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>You know how to reach me.
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>Is it time for good-byes already? I'm going to miss you...
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE1<tab>Thy will be done.
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE2<tab>The markets may be a bleedin' battlefield, but I'm a godsdamned soldier. You can count on me, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>.
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE3<tab>...
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE4<tab>Why so serrrious? <sigh> So it goes.
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE5<tab>I hardly think that warranted my personal appearance, but what is done is done.
target: TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE5<tab>当面、そっとしといてくれよ。

source: TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE6<tab>Then I have satisfied your every need? Excellent! I do so take pleasure in servicing my clients.
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>Good-bye for now, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sirrr)) /var>.
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>Right then, let's get on with it!
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>There is no call for concerrrn.
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>When the master's away, the cat will play.
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>Gods, this is tirin'...
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>You don't want to be with me anymore? <sniffle>
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE1<tab>I shall carry out your wishes as instructed, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>.
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE2<tab>Bwahahaha! I'm in yer bazaar, sellin' yer wares!
target: TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE2<tab>てやんでぇ、用済みってわけでぇ！

source: TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE3<tab>I will go now.
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE4<tab>Awww, bugger. Reckon I best get to work...
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE5<tab>I don't do good-byes.
target: TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE5<tab>オイラ、帰っていいんだな……帰るぞ。

source: TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE6<tab>Go and grab yourself some shut-eye, chief. You look terrible!
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>Will that be all for today, <var 08 E905 ((milady)) ((milord)) /var>? Understood.
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>Aye, aye, cap'n!
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>Duly noted.
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>Not exactly how I was hopin' to spend my day, but I suppose it can't be helped.
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>Ours is not to reason why. Ours is but to do and die.
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>Ever the consummate professional, I see. Another time, then.
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_AURA_MALE_TYPE1<tab>If there is nothing else, then I shall take my leave.
target:
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_AURA_MALE_TYPE1おっ、もう終いか？
なんかあったら、すぐ呼んでくれよ。

source: TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_AURA_MALE_TYPE2<tab>Is that all? Guess I'll be on my way, then.
target: TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_AURA_MALE_TYPE2<tab>遠慮は無用、いつでも呼びな！

source: TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_AURA_MALE_TYPE3<tab>Any last requests? Very well. Heh heh heh... Ahem.
target:
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_AURA_MALE_TYPE3ク……ククク……
ワーッハッハッハッハッハッハッグゲッ！
ゲッゲホッ……ゲホッ！

source: TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_AURA_MALE_TYPE4<tab>Ah, yes, of course. Duty calls!
target:
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_AURA_MALE_TYPE4じゃあ、またな。
次に呼ばれるまで、茶でも淹れて待つとするよ。

source: TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_AURA_MALE_TYPE5<tab>You are finished with me, then?
target:
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_AURA_MALE_TYPE5ん、終わったぁ？
ふわ～あ……そんじゃあな。

source:
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_AURA_MALE_TYPE6Here today and gone tomorrow;♪
Yes, I know─♪
That is so!♪
target:
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_AURA_MALE_TYPE6したらば、御免ッ！
次なる出番に備えておくからなーッハッハ！

source: TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>If ever you have need of me, just ring.
target:
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE1それでは、いってらっしゃいませ！
良い旅路となることを、願っておりますね。

source: TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>Always a pleasure, <var 08 E905 ((Mistress)) ((Master)) /var>.
target:
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE2そんじゃ、行ってきな！
冒険もいいけど、アタイのことを忘れたら承知しないよ！

source: TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>Right, then.
target:
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE3失礼するわ。
……また私を呼ぶこと、いいわね？

source: TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>Finished already? Guess that's that, then.
target: TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>ではでは、ご機嫌うるわしゅう～。

source: TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>You're leaving already? Fine, then! I-It's not like I wanted you to stay or anything.
target:
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE5もう……帰っていいの？
わたしなんかで、ごめんね……。

source: TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>Very good, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>! Very good indeed!
target:
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE6じゃあ、まったね～ん！
何かあったら、いつ呼んでくれてもいいよ。
気がむいたら来るからさっ！

source: TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE1<tab>Always a pleasure to serve, <var 08 E905 ((milady)) ((milord)) /var>.
target:
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE1の力になれたなら、本望さ。
またいつでも呼んでくれ。

source: TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE2<tab>Hmph. I hope that next time you will have a more meaningful task for me.
target:
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE2大した仕事じゃねぇや。
……また、いつでも呼べよ。

source: TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE3<tab><var 1A 02 /var>Good-bye<var 1A 01 /var>.
target:
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE3ほかに貴様の望みを満たせる者が、
果たしてどれほどいたものか？
……また呼ぶがいい。

source: TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE4<tab>And with that, I shall be off. Places to go, people to see.
target:
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE4それじゃ、失礼するよ。
さて、毛づくろいでもしようかな。

source: TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE5<tab>Bahahaha! Till next time, my friend!
target:
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE5……おう、そんじゃな。
ったく、いつでもズバッと呼びやがれよな！

source: TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE6<tab>Ring for me whenever you please! You know that I will never let you down!
target:
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_HROTHGAR_MALE_TYPE6へいへ～い！
気が向いたら、また呼んでちょーよ。

source: TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>Must we part so soon?
target:
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE1あら、もう行っちゃうの？
また呼んでね、ハニー♪

source: TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>And I am off!
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>Call on me as you please. If I am so inclined, I will answer.
target:
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE3請い願うことあらば、我を呼べ。
我もまた、汝とまみえんことを望もう……。

source: TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>That is all, I suppose...? <yawn> Very well...
target:
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE4んぅぅ……もうオシマイ、かな～？
オヤスミしてるから、また起こしてねぇ。

source: TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>That is all? Oh, I was hoping there'd be more...
target:
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE5ボクのこと、もう帰らせちゃうんだ？
ふーん……またね。

source: TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>Is that all you need of me? But I could yet serve you in so many ways!
target:
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_VIERA_FEMALE_TYPE6あら、もうお話は終わり？
つれないこと……。

source: TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_VIERA_MALE_TYPE1<tab>Do not hesitate to call upon me again. Fare you well in your endeavors, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>.
target:
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_VIERA_MALE_TYPE1きっとまた、力にならせてくれよ？
キミも……いってらっしゃい。

source: TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_VIERA_MALE_TYPE2<tab>Just say the word, yer <var 08 E905 ((ladyship)) ((lordship)) /var>, and I'll be here with bells on.
target:
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_VIERA_MALE_TYPE2のためにッてなら、
またいつでも馳せ参じるっすよ！！

source: TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_VIERA_MALE_TYPE3<tab>If you have no further need of my services...
target: TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_VIERA_MALE_TYPE3<tab>しからば、御免いたしましょう……。

source: TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_VIERA_MALE_TYPE4<tab>I'm off for another glass, then. You know where to find me!
target:
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_VIERA_MALE_TYPE4そんじゃ、また一杯やってっから！
いつでも呼んでくんなね。

source: TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_VIERA_MALE_TYPE5<tab>What─is that it? Are you <var 1A 02 /var>sure<var 1A 01 /var> you need a retainer?
target:
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_VIERA_MALE_TYPE5なんだよ～、もう終わりぃ？
それじゃ行くけどぉ……また呼べよな。

source: TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_VIERA_MALE_TYPE6<tab>Nothing else? Then I shall be hopping along.
target:
TEXT_HOUFURMERCHANT_00511_LEAVE_VIERA_MALE_TYPE6もう御用はお済みで？
そいじゃ、あっしは失礼するよ。
